albums.p: Were you married to her? ' ' Yes, of course I was, that's why it's so embarrassing to forget ... I think it was Varya ... or was it Manya? . . . no, Varya, that's it ...she wore a striped dress, worked at the museum. . . .No good, can't remember. So, she used to say, she had gone out that morning carrying those yellow flowers for me to find her at last and that if it hadn't happened she would have committed suicide because her life was empty.
